lines.text: Hisssssss! (Are you bringing thisss baby to challenge me? Eat my venom!)
Hisssss! Hiiiiiisssss! (That isss no ssserpent! Give it here, and I'll show that worm itsss place!)
Hissss... (I sssee you have no inferior ssspecimensss with you currently...)
Hiss? Hisssssssss! (Another? I mussst have it posssthassste!)
Hisssss? Hissssssss... (No more wormsss? I have conquered them all, then.)
